2025-05-30 00:38:17,701 - copilot_service - INFO - Answer: Contextual Understanding refers to the ability to comprehend and interpret a text by considering its surrounding context, including cultural, historical, and situational factors. This concept emphasizes the importance of analyzing a text within its broader framework to grasp its intended meaning and nuances.
