Concept 1:
2025-05-30 00:59:53,491 - copilot_service - INFO - Name: Maximum Subarray Sum
2025-05-30 00:59:53,492 - copilot_service - INFO - Definition: The largest possible sum of a contiguous subarray within a given array of integers, which can include both positive and negative numbers.
2025-05-30 00:59:53,492 - copilot_service - INFO - Application: Used in financial data analysis to identify the most profitable sequence of transactions or in sensor data processing to detect the longest period of positive readings.
