Flashcard 10:
2025-05-31 15:17:55,216 - copilot_service - INFO - Question: Why is amortized analysis useful for analyzing algorithms like Heap Sort?
2025-05-31 15:17:55,217 - copilot_service - INFO - Answer: Amortized analysis is useful for Heap Sort because it involves repeated calls to a data structure (heap) with varying operation times. By averaging the cost over all operations, amortized analysis provides an accurate estimate of the total running time, even if individual operations have different costs.
