Flashcard 8:
2025-06-01 11:44:32,297 - copilot_service - INFO - Question: What is the difference between NP-complete and NP-hard problems?
2025-06-01 11:44:32,298 - copilot_service - INFO - Answer: All NP-complete problems are NP-hard, but not all NP-hard problems are NP-complete. NP-complete problems are in NP, while NP-hard problems may not be.
