Concept 5:
2025-06-01 11:47:16,472 - copilot_service - INFO - Name: P and NP Classes
2025-06-01 11:47:16,472 - copilot_service - INFO - Definition: P-class problems are solvable in polynomial time by deterministic algorithms. NP-class problems are solvable in polynomial time by nondeterministic algorithms or verifiable in polynomial time.
2025-06-01 11:47:16,473 - copilot_service - INFO - Application: The Traveling Salesman Problem (TSP) is NP-complete, with applications in logistics and route optimization.
