Concept 6:
2025-06-01 11:47:16,474 - copilot_service - INFO - Name: Polynomial Reduction
2025-06-01 11:47:16,475 - copilot_service - INFO - Definition: Transforming one problem (L1) into another (L2) such that the solution to L2 provides the solution to L1 in polynomial time.
