Concept 5:
2025-06-01 11:55:42,476 - copilot_service - INFO - Name: P and NP Classes
2025-06-01 11:55:42,476 - copilot_service - INFO - Definition: P-class includes decision problems solvable in polynomial time by deterministic algorithms. NP-class includes problems solvable in polynomial time by nondeterministic algorithms or verifiable in polynomial time.
2025-06-01 11:55:42,477 - copilot_service - INFO - Application: Integer factorization is believed to be outside P but within NP, with applications in cryptography (e.g., RSA encryption).
2025-06-01 11:55:42,477 - copilot_service - INFO - Insight: Recent work by [Impagliazzo and Paturi (2021)](https://doi.org/10.1145/3406325.3451097) explored the relationship between P and NP, providing new insights into the complexity of SAT solvers.
