Flashcard 6:
2025-06-01 12:53:35,878 - copilot_service - INFO - Question: What is the difference between NP-complete and NP-hard?
2025-06-01 12:53:35,878 - copilot_service - INFO - Answer: NP-complete problems are both in NP and have all NP problems reducible to them. NP-hard problems only require that all NP problems are reducible to them, without needing to be in NP themselves.
