2025-06-01 12:59:15,254 - copilot_service - INFO - Insight: Recent research has focused on approximation algorithms for NP-complete problems. A 2021 study by Karlin et al. introduced a new approximation algorithm for the Traveling Salesman Problem with improved bounds, leveraging techniques from spectral graph theory (Karlin, Khot, and Saket, 2021).
