2025-06-01 12:59:15,257 - copilot_service - INFO - Application: Sorting algorithms (e.g., QuickSort, MergeSort) are tractable and widely used in data processing. In contrast, the Boolean Satisfiability Problem (SAT) is intractable and used in hardware and software verification.
