Concept 4:
2025-06-01 14:05:54,557 - copilot_service - INFO - Name: NP-Complete
2025-06-01 14:05:54,558 - copilot_service - INFO - Definition: A problem in NP that is as hard as the hardest problems in NP. Every problem in NP can be reduced to it in polynomial time.
2025-06-01 14:05:54,558 - copilot_service - INFO - Application: The Traveling Salesman Problem (TSP) is a classic NP-complete problem with applications in logistics and route optimization.
2025-06-01 14:05:54,559 - copilot_service - INFO - Insight: A recent paper by [Bansal et al., 2023] provided new insights into the approximability of NP-complete problems, particularly focusing on the TSP.
