2025-06-01 14:08:44,049 - copilot_service - INFO - Definition: An amortized analysis technique where each operation is assigned an amortized cost. If the amortized cost exceeds the actual cost, the difference is stored as credit, which can be used to cover operations where the actual cost exceeds the amortized cost.
