2025-06-03 23:47:19,914 - copilot_service - INFO - Definition: A transformation of one problem (L1) into another problem (L2) such that the solution to L2 can be used to solve L1 in polynomial time.
2025-06-03 23:47:19,915 - copilot_service - INFO - Application: Used in compiler optimization, where complex code is reduced to simpler problems that can be optimized more efficiently.
